e perroom sale of a hotel ever recorded in the city of boston genevaedit opened in  as the hôtel du rhone it was the first hotel built in europe after the second world war it was purchased by the mandarin oriental group in  and renovated in  located on the right bank of the rhone river in geneva it offers  guestrooms and  suites as well as three restaurants and bars guangzhouedit mandarin oriental guangzhou designed by interior designer tony chi opened in january  located adjacent to taikoo hui the mandarin oriental hotel has  guest rooms and suites four restaurants and bars a specialty cake shop and an expansive spa hong kong central victoriaedit main article mandarin oriental hong kong the hotel opened its doors in  as the mandarin hong kong the landmark victoriaedit located in the landmark office and shopping development in hong kong the landmark mandarin oriental is a forbes fivestar hotel with  of the largest guestrooms and suites in hong kong with an average size of  sq ft  m in addition to the rooms the hotel operates the  sq ft  m forbes fivestar oriental spa the mobar and the michelin twostarred amber restaurant hong kong the excelsior causeway bayedit main article the excelsior hong kong jakartaedit the mandarin oriental in jakarta is a fivestar luxury hotel located at thamrin road near the hotel indonesia roundabout construction of the hotel started in  and was opened on  september  as the mandarin the hotel was the last of the major hotels to be built during the s hotel boom period in jakarta the hotel maintained its status as a fivestar hotel throughout its history the mandarin oriental jakarta contains  rooms the hotel was renovated in  kuala lumpuredit mandarin oriental kuala lumpur the mandarin oriental in kuala lumpur malaysia opened in  and has  rooms  suites and  apartements it is located directly next to the petronas towers offers  restaurants and  bars a fitness center a spa and an infinity edge outdoor pool with views over the near located city center park it has been rated as the best hotel in kuala lumpur several times and as one of the  best hotels in malaysia the fivestar hotel is nationwide famous for its personal service the different culinary offers by international chefs and the room views over the illuminated petronas towers by night las vegasedit main article mandarin oriental las vegas mandarin oriental las vegas a forbes triple fivestar hotel opened december   located on the las vegas strip at the entrance to citycenter the story nongaming hotel has  guestrooms and suites a  sq ft  m spa and fitness center and  sq ft  m of function space also located on property are the signature restaurant twist by pierre gagnaire mozen bistro the tea lounge the mandarin bar and poolside café adjacent to the outdoor pool london hyde parkedit main article mandarin oriental hyde park london mandarin oriental hyde park london is located on hyde park in knightsbridge opposite harvey nichols department store originally opened as the hyde park hotel in  mandarin oriental hotel group purchased the property in  and reopened it as the mandarin oriental hyde park london in  today the hotel contains  rooms and suites and operates a spa and the two michelinstarred dinner by heston blumenthal macauedit mandarin oriental macau is a forbes fivestar hotel located in the one central development the hotel has  rooms and suites a restaurant lounge retail cake shop and a forbes fivestar spa madrid ritz hoteledit main article ritz hotel madrid mandarin oriental purchased this hotel in may  for  million and intends to renovate it at a cost of a further  million currently the madrid ritz operates under a separate brand although it is part of the mandarin oriental website miamiedit main article mandarin oriental miami mandarin oriental hotel group’s property in miami florida is located on brickell key a  acres  ha island in biscayne bay and operates  guestrooms and suites with views of the atlantic ocean biscayne bay and the miami skyline the hotel also has the azul and lamar restaurants a mobar  lounge private beach and the only forbes fivestar spa in the state of florida munichedit main article mandarin oriental munich formerly the hotel rafael munich mandarin oriental munich is located in munich’s old town near shopping along maximilianstrasse and the famous brewery hofbräuhaus new york cityedit asiate restaurant at mandarin oriental new york overlooking central park main article mandarin oriental new york mandarin oriental new york is a forbes fivestar located in the time warner center at columbus circle in manhattan set more than  feet  m above ground in the north tower the hotels  guestrooms and  suites all have views of central park the hudson river and new york citys upper west side the hotel operates asiate restaurant the lobby lounge mobar and one of only two forbes fivestar spas in new york parisedit main article mandarin oriental paris mandarin oriental paris is a luxury hotel in paris france the room hotel opened in june  in a restored art deco government ministry building the hotel has two restaurants and bars – including two establishments by michelin starwinning chef thierry marx – as well as the spa at mandarin oriental paris sanyaedit the groups first property in mainland china mandarin oriental sanya is located in hainan chinas southernmost island province opened in january  the  hectares resort operates  guestrooms suites and villas the hotel has five restaurants four bars three landscaped outdoor swimming pools and a  square metres  sq ft spa village nihonbashi mitsui tower and mandarin oriental tokyo singaporeedit main article mandarin oriental singapore mandarin oriental singapore is one of the mandarin oriental hotel group’s largest hotels with  guestrooms and suites the property is located in marina centre the hotel has five restaurants two bars a spa fitness center grand ballroom and thirteen individual meeting rooms the hotel opened in  it underwent a renovation completed in  taipeiedit mandarin oriental taipei opened in may  and is located in the heart of the city on dunhua north road taipei’s main boulevard tokyoedit mandarin oriental tokyo in japan is located between the th and th floors of the story nihonbashi mitsui tower has  guestrooms and suites overlooking the tokyo imperial palace garden to the west and tokyo bay to the southeast the hotel operates eight restaurants a bar lobby tea corner and retail cake shop among the restaurants is the michelinstarred sense serving modern variations of cantonese cuisine washington dcedit mandarin oriental washington dc the mandarin oriental washington dc is located in the southwest quadrant of the city many of the  guestrooms and  suites feature views eric ziebolds cityzen the hotels main restaurant was one of the citys fine dining options the more informal café mozu was replaced by souwester in  souwester was in turn replaced by muze in  former propertiesedit mandarin oriental ananda the himalayasedit opened as a fullservice destination spa ananda  in the himalayas was located in narendra nagar uttarakhand set in the indian himalayas it was operated briefly by mandarin oriental hotel group from  to  developed first by rafael hotels limited in partnership with indian hotels and health resorts ihhr the resort was launched by mandarin oriental hotel group after it acquired rafael hotels limited in  at the time rafael hotels consisted of six luxury hotels including the mark hotel in new york hôtel du rhône in geneva hotel rafael in munich and the turnberry isle resort  club in miami koh samuiedit the hotel is formerly known as mandarin oriental baan taling ngam located in koh samui thailand the hotel was later reflagged under the le meridien hotel group and is now operated under the intercontinental hotels group brand macauedit mandarin oriental macau the hotel was named the excelsior when it was first opened back in  it became the oriental hotel and subsequently the mandarin oriental hotel the hotel was purchased in  by part owner stanley ho and was renamed the grand lapa hotel macau ahead of the completion of current mandarin oriental macau hotel and serviced apartments in  the hotel was operated by the mandarin oriental hotel group until january   bela vista hotel macau in the late s the excelsior part of the mandarin oriental hotel group took out a year lease on the hotel from the macanese government the excelsior renovated the hotel between  when it reopened its capacity was drastically reduced to just  suites  rooms restaurant bar and function space and was run as a branch of the much larger mandarin oriental macau hotel it closed as a hotel on march   and was sold to portugal who converted it into the portuguese consul when macau was handed back to china in december  built in  originally as a residence for edward and catherine clarke a british captain and his wife who converted it into a hotel named “boa vista” in  manilaedit main article mandarin oriental manila formerly the mandarin manilacitation needed the hotel opened in  in makati city and was renamed mandarin oriental manila in the s the hotel had more than  rooms the hotel closed in september  with a replacement scheduled to open in  nearby in the makati area san franciscoedit main article mandarin oriental san francisco mandarin oriental san francisco occupied the top  floors of the story  california center office in the financial district of san francisco california the twin towers of the room hotel are situated at degree angles relative to the rest of the building with two glassy skybridges that offer views of the san francisco bay area in february  the hotel was sold to the loews hotel company surabayaedit formerly the majapahit hotel this indonesian historic hotel was thoroughly renovated into a fivestar hotel and operated by the mandarin oriental hotel group from  for about eight years as hotel majapahit surabaya chiang mai dhara dheviedit the hotel is formerly known as manda