otels limited was formed as a hotel management company with the intention to expand into asia that year the company acquired a  interest in the oriental hotel resulting in two flagship hotels for the company in  the company combined the two hotels under a common name mandarin oriental hotel group in  mandarin oriental hotel group was floated on the stock exchange of hong kong under the name of mandarin oriental international limited mandarin oriental international limited is incorporated in bermuda and listed in london singapore and bermuda mandarin oriental hotel group limited which operates from victoria city manages the activities of the group’s hotels mandarin oriental hotel group operates or has under development  hotels representing over  rooms in  countries with  hotels in asia  in the americas and  in europe and north africa in addition the group operates or has under development  residences at mandarin oriental connected to the group’s properties starting in september  mandarin oriental showed the moments of delight at mandarin oriental at all hotels in  this video was slightly updated to add new scenes and in  it featured lyrics by chinese singer sa ding ding current propertiesedit as of update mandarin oriental hotel group operates hotels in china czech republic france germany hong kong indonesia italy japan malaysia singapore switzerland spain turkey taiwan thailand the united kingdom united states and morocco  atlantaedit mandarin oriental atlanta is a fivestar hotel in the buckhead neighborhood of atlanta georgia the hotels  rooms and suites are housed in a story skyscraper designed by american architect robert a m stern occupying floors  to  are the residences at mandarin oriental atlanta homes managed by mandarin oriental bangkokedit main article mandarin oriental bangkok mandarin oriental bangkok is a fivestar hotel in bangkok thailand on the eastern bank of the chao phraya river today the hotel is one of two flagship properties of mandarin oriental