ase on the hotel from the macanese government the excelsior renovated the hotel between  when it reopened its capacity was drastically reduced to just  suites  rooms restaurant bar and function space and was run as a branch of the much larger mandarin oriental macau hotel it closed as a hotel on march   and was sold to portugal who converted it into the portuguese consul when macau was handed back to china in december  built in  originally as a residence for edward and catherine clarke a british captain and his wife who converted it into a hotel named “boa vista” in  manilaedit main article mandarin oriental manila formerly the mandarin manilacitation needed the hotel opened in  in makati city and was renamed mandarin oriental manila in the s the hotel had more than  rooms the hotel closed in september  with a replacement scheduled to open in  nearby in the makati area san franciscoedit main article mandarin oriental san francisco mandarin oriental san francisco occupied the top  floors of the story  california center office in the financial district of san francisco california the twin towers of the room hotel are situated at degree angles relative to the rest of the building with two glassy skybridges that offer views of the san francisco bay area in february  the hotel was sold to the loews hotel company surabayaedit formerly the majapahit hotel this indonesian historic hotel was thoroughly renovated into a fivestar hotel and operated by the mandarin oriental hotel group from  for about eight years as hotel majapahit surabaya chiang mai dhara dheviedit the hotel is formerly known as mandarin dhara dhevi located in chiang mai thailand proposed propertiesedit as of update hotels are under development in abu dhabi beijing beirut boca raton doha chengdu chongqing costa rica denpasarbali dellis cay dubai grand cayman honolulu istanbul maldives manila marbella moscow melbourne and shenzhen incidentsedit leslie cheung suicide edit on  april  singer actor and film producer leslie cheung leapt to his death from the th floor of the mandarin oriental in central hong kong every year on the anniversary of his death a fanorganised memorial event takes place outside the hotel beijing fire edit main article beijing television cultural center fire on  february  the beijing television cultural center which was to incorporate a mandarin oriental hotel caught fire due to unauthorized fireworks celebrating the chinese new year the structure was severely damaged but did not collapse and is now under repair one fireman died from the incident credit card breach edit in march  a number of mandarin oriental hotels were affected by a pointofsale systems security breach referencesedit  a b c d e f corporate information press kit mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    the mandarin oriental bangkok the most famous hotels in the world retrieved  march    httpswwwyoutubecomwatchvpnhlxoskxq  httpswwwyoutubecomwatchvfknvzsuii  awardwinning hotels  resorts in asia europe  the americas mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    mandarin oriental atlanta brings unsurpassed luxury and service to atlanta’s acclaimed buckhead neighborhood mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    mandarin oriental bangkok  overview mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    ranking de las calles comerciales más caras de españa en  tabla idealistacom retrieved    a b mandarin oriental barcelona  fact sheet mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    mandarin oriental barcelona  did you know mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    mandarin oriental bodrum offers new wellness retreats retrieved  may    forbes travel guide  four star restaurants forbes travel guide  retrieved    mandarin oriental boston  fact sheet mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    carlock catherine  luxury hotel group to buy mandarin oriental for m highest perroom price ever in boston boston business journal retrieved    history of mandarin oriental geneva mandarinorientalcom   luxury evolved 