 for the company in  the company combined the two hotels under a common name mandarin oriental hotel group in  mandarin oriental hotel group was floated on the stock exchange of hong kong under the name of mandarin oriental international limited mandarin oriental international limited is incorporated in bermuda and listed in london singapore and bermuda mandarin oriental hotel group limited which operates from victoria city manages the activities of the group’s hotels mandarin oriental hotel group operates or has under development  hotels representing over  rooms in  countries with  hotels in asia  in the americas and  in europe and north africa in addition the group operates or has under development  residences at mandarin oriental connected to the group’s properties starting in september  mandarin oriental showed the moments of delight at mandarin oriental at all hotels in  this video was slightly updated to add new scenes and in  it featured lyrics by chinese singer sa ding ding current propertiesedit as of update mandarin oriental hotel group operates hotels in china czech republic france germany hong kong indonesia italy japan malaysia singapore switzerland spain turkey taiwan thailand the united kingdom united states and morocco  atlantaedit mandarin oriental atlanta is a fivestar hotel in the buckhead neighborhood of atlanta georgia the hotels  rooms and suites are housed in a story skyscraper designed by american architect robert a m stern occupying floors  to  are the residences at mandarin oriental atlanta homes managed by mandarin oriental bangkokedit main article mandarin oriental bangkok mandarin oriental bangkok is a fivestar hotel in bangkok thailand on the eastern bank of the chao phraya river today the hotel is one of two flagship properties of mandarin oriental hotel group barcelonaedit mandarin oriental barcelona is a hotel in barcelona spain is located on passeig de grácia regarded by some calculations as the most expensive street in spain previously the location of the barcelona head office of the banco hispanico americano the avantgarde hotel has  guestrooms and suites a  m  sq ft spa and fitness center with an indoor lap pool a restaurant a rooftop terrace with a dipping pool and private function rooms bodrumedit mandarin oriental bodrum is located on a  hectare waterfront site on the northern side of the turkish peninsula built on a series of levels in the hillside the resort has  guestrooms and suites all with sundecks terraces or balconies and some with private gardens and pools the resort also has  restaurants and bars and a  square meter spa the entrance to mandarin oriental boston as a pace truck for the  boston marathon passes by bostonedit mandarin oriental boston located on boylston street in the back bay neighborhood opened in october  a forbes fivestar and aaa fivediamond hotel it has  guestrooms and  suites and a forbes four star restaurant and the m bar  lounge in addition to the guestrooms and suites the hotel operates  condominiums and  apartments each with access to hotel amenities such as housekeeping inroom dining a concierge and a  sq ft  m forbes fivestar spa  fitness center in january  it was reported that the mandarin oriental hotel group international ltd planned to purchase the hotel and unit luxury condominium building from cwb hotel lp for  million the cost of this deal would be  perroom making this the most expensive perroom sale of a hotel ever recorded in the city of boston genevaedit opened in  as the hôtel du rhone it was the first hotel built in europe after the second world war it was purchased by the mandarin oriental group in  and renovated in  located on the right bank of the rhone river in geneva it offers  guestrooms and  suites as well as three restaurants and bars guangzhouedit mandarin oriental guangzhou designed by interior designer tony chi opened in january  located adjacent to taikoo hui the mandarin oriental hotel has  guest rooms and suites four restaurants 