olumbus circle in manhattan set more than  feet  m above ground in the north tower the hotels  guestrooms and  suites all have views of central park the hudson river and new york citys upper west side the hotel operates asiate restaurant the lobby lounge mobar and one of only two forbes fivestar spas in new york parisedit main article mandarin oriental paris mandarin oriental paris is a luxury hotel in paris france the room hotel opened in june  in a restored art deco government ministry building the hotel has two restaurants and bars – including two establishments by michelin starwinning chef thierry marx – as well as the spa at mandarin oriental paris sanyaedit the groups first property in mainland china mandarin oriental sanya is located in hainan chinas southernmost island province opened in january  the  hectares resort operates  guestrooms suites and villas the hotel has five restaurants four bars three landscaped outdoor swimming pools and a  square metres  sq ft spa village nihonbashi mitsui tower and mandarin oriental tokyo singaporeedit main article mandarin oriental singapore mandarin oriental singapore is one of the mandarin oriental hotel group’s largest hotels with  guestrooms and suites the property is located in marina centre the hotel has five restaurants two bars a spa fitness center grand ballroom and thirteen individual meeting rooms the hotel opened in  it underwent a renovation completed in  taipeiedit mandarin oriental taipei opened in may  and is located in the heart of the city on dunhua north road taipei’s main boulevard tokyoedit mandarin oriental tokyo in japan is located between the th and th floors of the story nihonbashi mitsui tower has  guestrooms and suites overlooking the tokyo imperial palace garden to the west and tokyo bay to the southeast the hotel operates eight restaurants a bar lobby tea corner and retail cake shop among the restaurants is the michelinstarred sense serving modern variations of cantonese cuisine washington dcedit mandarin oriental washington dc the mandarin oriental washington dc is located in the southwest quadrant of the city many of the  guestrooms and  suites feature views eric ziebolds cityzen the hotels main restaurant was one of the citys fine dining options the more informal café mozu was replaced by souwester in  souwester was in turn replaced by muze in  former propertiesedit mandarin oriental ananda the himalayasedit opened as a fullservice destination spa ananda  in the himalayas was located in narendra nagar uttarakhand set in the indian himalayas it was operated briefly by mandarin oriental hotel group from  to  developed first by rafael hotels limited in partnership with indian hotels and health resorts ihhr the resort was launched by mandarin oriental hotel group after it acquired rafael hotels limited in  at the time rafael hotels consisted of six luxury hotels including the mark hotel in new york hôtel du rhône in geneva hotel rafael in munich and the turnberry isle resort  club in miami koh samuiedit the hotel is formerly known as mandarin oriental baan taling ngam located in koh samui thailand the hotel was later reflagged under the le meridien hotel group and is now operated under the intercontinental hotels group brand macauedit mandarin oriental macau the hotel was named the excelsior when it was first opened back in  it became the oriental hotel and subsequently the mandarin oriental hotel the hotel was purchased in  by part owner stanley ho and was renamed the grand lapa hotel macau ahead of the completion of current mandarin oriental macau hotel and serviced apartments in  the hotel was operated by the mandarin oriental hotel group until january   bela vista hotel macau in the late s the excelsior part of the mandarin oriental hotel group took out a year lease on the hotel from the macanese government the excelsior renovated the hotel between  when it reopened its capacity was drastically reduced to just  suites  rooms restaurant bar and function space and was run as a branch of the much larger mandarin oriental macau hotel it closed as a hotel on march   and was sold to portugal who converted it into the portuguese consul when macau was handed back to china in december  built in  originally as a residence for edward and catherine clarke a british captain and his wife who converted it into a hotel named “boa vista” in  manilaedit main article mandarin oriental manila formerly the mandarin manilacitation needed the hotel opened in  in makati city and was renamed mandarin oriental manila in the s the hotel had more than  rooms the hotel closed in september  with a replacement scheduled to open in  nearby in the makati area san franciscoedit main article mandarin oriental san francisco mandarin oriental san francisco occupied the top  floors of the story  california center office in the financial district of san francisco california the twin towers of the room hotel are situated at degree angles relative to the rest of the building with two glassy skybridges that offer views of the san francisco bay area in february  the hotel was sold to the loews hotel company surabayaedit formerly the majapahit hotel this indonesian historic hotel was thoroughly renovated into a fivestar hotel and operated by the mandarin oriental hotel group from  for about eight years as hotel majapahit surabaya chiang mai dhara dheviedit the hotel is formerly known as mandarin dhara dhevi located in chiang mai thailand proposed propertiesedit as of update hotels are under development in abu dhabi beijing beirut boca raton doha chengdu chongqing costa rica denpasarbali dellis cay dubai grand cayman honolulu istanbul maldives manila marbella moscow melbourne and shenzhen incidentsedit leslie cheung suicide edit on  april  singer actor and film producer leslie cheung leapt to his death from the th floor of the mandarin oriental in central hong kong every year on the anniversary of his death a fanorganised memorial event takes place outside the hotel beijing fire edit main article beijing television cultural center fire on  february  the beijing television cultural center which was to incorporate a mandarin oriental hotel caught fire due to unauthorized fireworks celebrating the chinese new year the structure was severely damaged but did not collapse and is now under repair one fireman died from the incident credit card breach edit in march  a number of mandarin oriental hotels were affected by a pointofsale systems security breach referencesedit  a b c d e f corporate information press kit mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    the mandarin oriental bangkok the most famous hotels in the world retrieved  march    httpswwwyoutubecomwatchvpnhlxoskxq  httpswwwyoutubecomwatchvfknvzsuii  awardwinning hotels  resorts in asia europe  the americas mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    mandarin oriental atlanta brings unsurpassed luxury and service to atlanta’s acclaimed buckhead neighborhood mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    mandarin oriental bangkok  overview mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    ranking de las calles comerciales más caras de españa en  tabla idealistacom retrieved    a b mandarin oriental barcelona  fact sheet mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    mandarin oriental barcelona  did you know mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    mandarin oriental bodrum offers new wellness retreats retrieved  may    forbes travel guide  four star restaurants forbes travel guide  retrieved    mandarin oriental boston  fact sheet mandarin oriental hotel group  retrieved    carlock catherine  luxury hotel group to buy mandarin oriental for m highest perroom price ever in boston boston business journal retrieved    history of mandarin oriental geneva mandarinorientalcom   luxury evolved the mandarin oriental geneva haute living  retrieved    geneva fine dining  mandarin oriental hotel geneva wwwmandarinorientalcom retrieved    three down one to go mandarin oriental opens in 